<note n="0296001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0296001">「造塔」，底本為 thūpaṁ kārāpitā ahaṁ，今採用脚註所出異本之 thūpakārāpika ahaṁ。</note>
<note n="0299001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0299001">底本為 Ekapiṇḍadāyikā，今採用暹羅本之 Ekapiṇḍapātadāyikā。</note>
<note n="0300002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0300002">「黃巾」，底本為 mahānelena，今採用暹羅本之 pitacolena。</note>
<note n="0304001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0304001">「見」，底本為 dasuṁ，今採用暹羅本之 daṭṭhuṁ。</note>
